  <section class="service-content section-spacing">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <h2>What is Pancafit?</h2>
      <p>Pancafit is a revolutionary postural correction method that addresses the root causes of pain and postural dysfunction. Using a patented device developed in Italy, this technique works with your body's natural muscle chains and fascial connections to restore proper alignment and eliminate chronic pain.</p>

